Package: austintexas.gov
Title: City of Austin Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for City of Austin Socrata Open Data portal
    (data.austintexas.gov). Provides discovery, search, and data access for
    crime reports, 311 requests, food inspections, traffic, and permits.
